Interface IConnection

Describes the properties of a physical connection that was established between the system and a Jabra.NET.Sdk device.

ParentConnectionId

Optional parameter pointing at a parent connection (if the current connection is established through such a parent connection), e.g. a wireless connection through a Jabra.NET.Sdk dongle device. In case the current connection is for a parent connection, the value of this optional property will be null.
